You will need to add something like the following to your .emacs file to
autoload the CMake mode for Emacs.

  (setq auto-mode-alist
            (append
             '(("CMakeLists\\.txt\\'" . cmake-mode))
             '(("\\.cmake\\'" . cmake-mode))
             auto-mode-alist))

  (autoload 'cmake-mode "${LISPDIR}/cmake-mode.el" t)

===========================================================================
